            <title>[CASSANDRA-2259] column values are only being validated in insert()</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-2259</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;insert() is the only code path that currently results in validate() being called for column values; it is possible to write invalid column values using batch_mutate()&lt;/p&gt;</description>
